        "items": [
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Back in Action</h1>Using a Shield Charge or Patch Kit briefly increases your weapons' read and reload speed."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Ballistic Resistance</h1>Reduces incoming UESC damage from ballistic weapons."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Bedside Manner</h1>While a crew member is nearby, your <b>Self-Repair Speed</b> is increased and you use healing consumables more quickly."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Carnage Cartridge</h1>Reloading after defeating a hostile overflows your magazine."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Clean Slate</h1>After reviving a crew member, nearby crew members are cleansed of MCH and OS status effects."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Dr. Killjoy</h1><b>Finisher Siphon</b> restores health and shields after finishing a Runner."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Logic Bomb</h1>Precision UESC eliminations <hack> nearby hostiles."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Muscular Augments</h1>While under the effects of Cardio Kick, your sprint speed is faster."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Overclocked Cooling</h1>While under the benefits of a Mechanic's Kit or OS Debug, gain increased <b>Heat Capacity.</b>"
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Stolen Intel</h1>Defeating a UESC commander ping nearby hostiles."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Sympathetic Reflex</h1>Defeating a hostile grants increased ADS speed and weapon handling to you and nearby crew members."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Thermal Sinks</h1>Sliding in water generates no heat."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Volt Resistance</h1>Reduces incoming UESC damage from volt weapons."
            },
            {
                "quality": "standard",
                "description": "<h1>Walk It Off</h1>While you are affected by any negative status effect, defeating a hostile cleanses the effect."
            }
        ]
    },
